<TEXT>&#2;<DATELINE>2011-04-01</DATELINE><TITLE>XMRV as a Human Pathogen?</TITLE><BODY>XMRV has been proposed to be associated with Prostate Cancer and Chronic Fatigue Syndrome. This proposition has been controversial because many investigators have failed to replicate the reported associations. Here, we explore whether XMRV is an authentic human pathogen in the light of recent findings that indicate otherwise.&#3;</BODY></TEXT>